In these uncertain times, we are simplifying the rebooking process for canceled flights.
SAMPLE LETTER TO AIRLINES:Here's a good form letter you can use to contact the airline-- fill in the blanks with your personal situation, flight and card info:Dear (INSERT AIRLINE NAME)I am/was scheduled to depart (INSERT DATE) from/to (INSERT CITY PAIR) on (INSERT AIRLINE).
(INSERT AIRLINE) informed me on (INSERT DATE) that my flights were canceled and offered me a credit for a future flight.